{"title":"金山岭长城","authors":["乔延凤"],"dates":[{"year":1992,"month":10,"day":20}],"parts":[{"type":"paragraph","text":"金山岭长城"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"乔延凤"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"山脊上飞动的城"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"把天的威严压低"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"塞南塞北　一墙之隔"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"草木也沾着边声"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"四顾仍旧人烟稀少"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"几朵飘逸的白云"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"轻浮于紫色的金山岭之巅"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"一如当年镇守崖口的戚继光"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"坐骑的鬣鬃"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"因思念自己的家乡"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"与身边戍守的山岭叠映"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"满眼葱茏的　分明"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"是骠悍骁勇的登州戍卒"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"比燕山还重的乡情"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"夏日　又登上金山岭长城"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"四百五十年的烟云轻轻飘过"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"只剩下一个伟大的民族"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"一个统一的国家"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"世代守卫的"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"一片安宁"}],"comments":[],"comment_pivots":[],"description":"","page_start":8,"page_end":8}